data.description: Wonderful Cape Cod in Desirable Millwood Neighborhood. Mid County Gloucester. Seller is currently updating wall color in Dining Room and Primary bathroom to light gray. This home offers many possibilities for use. Nice floor plan & great for entertaining. Main Level includes a spacious Living room with a Gas Fireplace. 3 year old Attached Deck with Sweeping views of the yard and wooded area offering Summer relaxing and Morning Cups of Coffee. Second floor includes Primary Bedroom with large walk in closet. Lower level has a large open space for a family room or a bedroom. Garage/workshop area on this level, too. Oversized water heater. Near to Amenities and a short drive to Peninsula Military Bases. Hurry to make this your NextHome!
